    <h1>RADBot – Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
    <p>RADBot does not collect, store or share any personal data. No user information is logged or retained beyond the current bot session.</p>

    <h2>2. Voice & Text Channels</h2>
    <p>RADBot only reads slash commands directed at it. It does not read, store or process any other messages or voice data.</p>

    <h2>3. Third Party Services</h2>
    <p>RADBot streams audio from publicly available radio stations. We are not responsible for the content or availability of these streams.</p>

    <h2>4. Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy concerns, contact <strong>.schorsch</strong> on Discord.</p>
